Package com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request.impl

Class Summary
ApacheSOAPRequester Singleton implementation of SOAPRequester, using the Apache HTTP Client
ListRequestImpl<ResultType,SOAPFaultType> Implementation of ListRequest
RequestFactoryImpl Factory for requests - retains a single instance of SOAPRequester to save object creation.
RequestImpl<ResultType,SOAPFaultType> Implementation of Request A RequestImpl, in essence, is a composition of a SOAPEnvelope for the request, a IceSoapParser for the response, and some code to to the post.
Response Encapsulates the details of a response from an SOAP request
SOAP11ListRequestImpl<ResultType> Extension of ListRequestImpl that defaults the SOAPFaultType to SOAP11Fault
SOAP11RequestImpl<ResultType> Extension of RequestImpl that defaults the SOAPFaultType to SOAP11Fault.
